statement.p:
Let f(x)=3^x and g(x)=\log_3{(x)}

Compute f(4)

Compute g\left[f(4)\right]

Compute \log_3{(3^{1.8})}

Compute \log_3{(3^{a})}

Let f(x)=\log_2{(x)} and g(x)=2^x

Compute f(32)

Compute g\left[f(32)\right]

Compute 2^{\log_2{(6)}}

Compute 2^{\log_2{(Q)}}

